{"tid":1322854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商場指警已取手令取閉路電視片段","createTime":"2019-07-16T05:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T05:45:43.000Z","uid":149471,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce936b58aab51c70f181c573366b8bcc6bc0a7e6","tid":1322854,"uid":149471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"商場指警已取手令取閉路電視片段<br />\n2019/07/16 13:05<br />\n沙田新城市廣場星期日爆發警民衝突，多人受傷。新城市指警方已取得手令，將向商場索取閉路電視片段。 <br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場服務處昨日接獲警方通知，指已取得裁判官發出手令，要求索取衝突當日的閉路電視錄影片段，服務處徵詢法律意見後，會按要求提交。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新鴻基地產早前發聲明指，新城市不知悉警方星期日傍晚進入商場內的行動，以及鐵路一度暫停服務的安排。昨晚有逾百名市民不滿商場容許警員進入造成混亂，在商場詢問處要求管理層解釋，商場職員向在場人士派發查詢表格<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552717/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4%E5%8F%96%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552717%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXkngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=398b81b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552717%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%258F%2596%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5&h=32620a3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552717/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%96%E6%89%8B%E4%BB%A4%E5%8F%96%E9%